  <h1>Locally owned dance school, offering seasonal, community-driven dance classes for children ages ~2-6</h1>
  <h2 class="title">Our Story</h2>
  <p>
    JP Dance Co-op is a locally owned dance school, offering seasonal, 
    community-driven dance classes for children ages ~2-6 at Spontaneous Celebrations 
    in Jamaica Plain. The school was created in 2017 by Caitlin Fisher, who wanted to 
    share her passion for dance by creating a series of dance programs that introduced 
    young children to movement. Classes are meant to be structured yet fun, offering room 
    for movement exploration.  
  </p>

  <h2 class="title">Instructors</h2>
  <div class="bio">
    <div class="bio__headshot">
